data.description: Entire house has been fully remodeled: kitchen, utility room, all bedrooms, both bathrooms, and the garage. New (2021) architectural design metal roof by Roser with 50 year warranty. New (2022) PEX plumbing. New (2022) electrical outlets and panels. New (2019) all aluminum A/C system with 10 year warranty. New (2022) garage door electrical motor, sensors, remote openers, and rubber seal at bottom of door. New (2022) attic insulation and ladder. New (2020) lawn and irrigation. Recent (May 2022) dryer vent maintenance. Having these systems in new condition is intrinsic to a sound investment.   All new appliances. All new lighting. 20 inch Italian porcelain tile throughout all main floors, bathroom floors, and shower walls. Custom designed full masonry Keystone fireplace. Pecky Cypress paneling. Security safe. All closets have ventilated wood shelving. 1,000 sf screened lanai with “Bullfrog” brand hot tub. 2 inch natural stone (Arizona Red) flagging on facade, landing, and chimney. For only $210 in annual homeowner's dues, NO monthly maintenance fees, a huge lot, and lake and golf course views make this neighborhood the very last of its kind, and Naples' best kept secret.
